Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
CBRE, in conjunction with Bosisto Commercial, are pleased to offer 2-4 Mephan Street, Maribyrnong, for sale and lease.

The property features a two-level temperature controlled office with a concrete tilt panel warehouse.
 
2-4 Mephan Street sits on a significant land holding with full drive around access. The prominent two-level corporate office faces Mephan Street with under croft car parking as well as off street car parking at the front of the site.

The site has a high clearance warehouse and is accessed by 8 roller doors around the perimeter and a smaller warehouse at the rear of the site. There is a hardstand area at the rear of the site which can be used for container storage and truck or car parking. This functional site has two street frontages to both Mephan Street and Birdwood Street.

Features include: 
+ Total land area: 14,900sqm*
+ Total building area: 8,364sqm*
+ Office & amenities: 1,116sqm*
+ Main warehouse: 6,604sqm*
+ Rear warehouse: 601sqm*
+ Canopy: 288sqm*
+ Rear yard hardstand: 2,500sqm*
+ Roller doors: 8
+ Ample on-site parking

*approx.

+1.21HA* elevated trophy corner landholding

+Quality large established warehouse / office improvements over two (2) levels comprising 8,265sqm* with fifteen (15) on-site car spaces suited to occupy or offering sizeable income potential

+Highly flexible Mixed-Use Zone with favourable height allowance for a major high density development (STCA) 

+Bolstered by significant frontages of 80m* to Raleigh Road and 87m* to Rosamond Road with multiple access and egress points

+Outstanding position directly adjacent to Highpoint Shopping Centre which is Australia’s 6th largest (featuring over 500 specialty fashion, homewares and lifestyle stores)

+Absolutely every form of retail, lifestyle & service offerings available including the picturesque Maribyrnong River 1km*, 2.7km* to Flemington Racecourse, 3km* to Moonee Ponds Activity Centre precinct, 9km* to Melbourne Airport and 7km* to Melbourne’s CBD 

191 Rosamond Road (Cnr Raleigh Road), Maribyrnong is For Sale Via Public Expressions of Interest Closing Thursday 14th October at 2:00pm (AEDT)

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:

Property features include:
+ Building areas: 800 - 2237*

+ Flexible Commercial 2 Zone
+ Suit a range of uses, including bulky goods retail and commercial
